OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FThe chairman of the has stepped down
OL,7,Famid ongoing tensions in the wake of
OL,8,Fthe Horizon IT scandal.
OL,10,FHenry Staunton will depart from the
OL,11,Frole following a phone call with
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch on
OL,13,FSaturday.
OL,15,FAn interim will be appointed
OL,16,F"shortly", the Department for Business
OL,17,Fand Trade said.
