OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FMr Staunton only took up the post at
OL,7,Fthe state-owned company in December
OL,8,F2022, following nine years as chairman
OL,9,Fof WH Smith.
OL,11,FHe had been tasked with leading the
OL,12,Fboard of directors as the business
OL,13,Freels from the fallout of what has
OL,14,Fbeen described as the UK's biggest
OL,15,Fmiscarriage of justice.
