OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FMr Staunton's departure follows
OL,7,Ffrustration in Whitehall over the
OL,8,Fcompany's governance, including a row
OL,9,Fover the prospective appointment of a
OL,10,Fnew senior independent director, Sky
OL,11,FNews reported.
OL,13,FInsiders told the outlet his exit was
OL,14,Fnot directly related to the Horizon
OL,15,Fscandal itself, but that there had
OL,16,Fbeen differences of opinion between
OL,17,Fhim and Government as to the best
OL,18,Fcandidate for the job.
