OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FIt comes at one of the most turbulent
OL,7,Fpoints in the company's history, with
OL,8,Fa statutory inquiry into the saga
OL,9,Funder way and renewed public anger
OL,10,Ffollowing its dramatisation in ITV's
OL,11,FMr Bates Vs the Post Office earlier
OL,12,Fthis month.
OL,14,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has also
OL,15,Fannounced blanket legislation to
OL,16,Fexonerate those wrongly prosecuted
OL,17,Fafter the TV series returned the
OL,18,Fscandal to the spotlight.
