OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "In a
OL,7,Fphone call earlier today, the
OL,8,FSecretary of State for Business and
OL,9,FTrade and Henry Staunton, chair of
OL,10,FPost Office Limited (POL), agreed to
OL,11,Fpart ways with mutual consent.
OL,13,F"An interim will be appointed shortly
OL,14,Fand a recruitment process for a new
OL,15,Fchair will be launched in due course,
OL,16,Fin accordance with the Governance Code
OL,17,Ffor Public Appointments."
